CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 26, 1955, pg. 11, reads: "DELTAS PLAN - Making extensive plans for sorors who are coming here from Ohio State University for a visit are these charming Pittsburgh Delta Sigma Theta sorors. One of the fetes planned is a party to be given by the graduate chapter in Joyce Bryant Room at the Flamingo.  Pictured, center, Justine Robinson; first row: Teddi Wofford and Vivian Swaine. Second row: Mrs. Christine Johnson, Irene Williams and Ann Perkins.  Top: Vivian Lane and Mildred Jefferson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Delta Sigma Theta sorority including Justine Robinson in center; second row: Teddi Wofford wearing polka dot dress, Viviane Swaine; third row: Christine Johnson, Irene Williams, Ann Perkins; fourth row: Vivian Lane and Mildred Jefferson, posed in interior with geometric doorways
